ion to do something really spectacular.” Vanguard News Nigeria U.S. President Donald Trump in a rare and unexpected gesture on Saturday, expressed his appreciation to the media organisations for making his Friday’s inauguration as the 45th President a “fantastic” one. Trump’s surprising gratitude to the media came after several months of adversarial relationship between him and the news outlets.… January 21, 2017 In "News" World leaders condemn 'assault on democracy' at US Capitol World leaders and governments on Wednesday expressed shock and outrage at the storming of the US Capitol in Washington by supporters of President Donald Trump. - Britain - British Prime Minister Boris Johnson on Twitter condemned the "disgraceful scenes in U.S.… January 7, 2021 In "Foreign" The U.S. President-elect, Donald Trump, made his maiden speech on Wednesday, praising his rival Democratic nominee, Hillary Clinton and pledging to unite America. November 9, 2016 In "News"